description:

If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

HAUTE COUTURE

Bonjour Mesdames, Mesdemoiselles, et Messieurs,

Welcome to the world of Haute Couture.

I have released this LoRA so you can all enjoy the best possible fashion on your characters.

As you can see on the pictures, this LoRA works well, but I have to advise you, it will not work on its own!

You will need to use proper wording and good prompts in order to make the most of it! It is quite unruly with colors, so pay attention.

Download this LoRA and get ready for the fashion show!
